<h2>Why People Are Buying Always Pan 2.0</h2>
<p>Kitchen clutter is real. Many people have too many pots and pans that they rarely use, especially in small apartments. The Always Pan became popular because it promises to replace eight pieces of cookware with one beautiful pan.</p>

<h2>What Is Always Pan 2.0?</h2>
<p>The Always Pan 2.0 is a 10.5-inch ceramic-coated pan with a steamer basket, built-in spoon rest, and pour spouts. It's designed for braising, searing, steaming, straining, sautéing, frying, boiling, and serving. It went viral through Instagram aesthetic appeal and influencer partnerships.</p>
<p><strong>Why it went viral:</strong> Instagram aesthetics and minimalist kitchen trend appeal</p>

<h2>How to Use Always Pan 2.0</h2>
<ol>
    <li><strong>1.</strong> Season the pan by heating a thin layer of oil over medium heat for 2 minutes before first use</li>
    <li><strong>2.</strong> Cook on low to medium heat — ceramic coating doesn't require high heat for nonstick performance</li>
    <li><strong>3.</strong> Use the included steamer basket for vegetables, dumplings, or reheating</li>
    <li><strong>4.</strong> Hand wash with a soft sponge — avoid abrasive cleaners to preserve the ceramic coating</li>
</ol>

